---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Use Cases | FennaAI"
  description="Discover how people use FennaAI to create, learn, and work smarter with their own personal AI."
>
  <div class="use-cases-page">
    <header class="page-header" data-animate-on-scroll>
      <h1>Imagine What You Could Build</h1>
      <p>
        FennaAI isn’t just another chatbot. It’s your own AI — trained on your
        files, your notes, your world. See how people are already using it.
      </p>
    </header>

    <main class="use-case-grid">
      <div class="use-case-card" data-animate-on-scroll>
        <h2>Writers & Creators</h2>
        <p>
          Turn your AI into a creative partner who knows your voice and never
          runs out of ideas.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Brainstorm fresh plot twists</li>
          <li>Develop dialogue in your style</li>
          <li>Refine drafts with instant feedback</li>
          <li>Summarize messy research notes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="use-case-card" data-animate-on-scroll>
        <h2>Professionals & Teams</h2>
        <p>
          Give your business a private assistant that understands your workflows
          — no cloud, no leaks.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Query internal documents</li>
          <li>Draft reports in your brand’s voice</li>
          <li>Summarize meetings automatically</li>
          <li>Turn raw data into clear insights</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="use-case-card" data-animate-on-scroll>
        <h2>Students & Researchers</h2>
        <p>
          Study smarter with an AI that actually knows your material — because
          you trained it.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Explain tough concepts clearly</li>
          <li>Chat directly with your PDFs</li>
          <li>Build custom study guides</li>
          <li>Spot inconsistencies in notes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="use-case-card" data-animate-on-scroll>
        <h2>Everyday Life</h2>
        <p>
          Your life, your data, your AI. A personal assistant that grows with
          you.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Plan meals with your recipes</li>
          <li>Organize travel plans</li>
          <li>Track new hobbies</li>
          <li>Reflect on journal entries</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </main>

    <section class="how-to-section">
      <div class="section-header" data-animate-on-scroll>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Two simple steps and you’re set.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-to-steps" data-animate-on-scroll>
        <div class="how-to-card">
          <h3>1. Pick an AI</h3>
          <p>
            Browse the library and grab a base AI — a generalist, a writer, a
            researcher, whatever fits you best.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-to-card">
          <h3>2. Train It</h3>
          <p>
            Upload your files, notes, or PDFs. In minutes, you’ve got a personal
            AI that actually knows your stuff.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section" data-animate-on-scroll>
      <h2>Your AI, Your Way</h2>
      <a href="/models" class="cta-button">Start Building Now</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .use-cases-page {
    max-width: 80rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .page-header,
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1rem 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1,
  .section-header h2,
  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-12);
  }

  .page-header p,
  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-11);
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .use-case-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .use-case-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .use-case-card {
    background: var(--gray-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-6);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .use-case-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .use-case-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .use-case-card p {
    color: var(--gray-11);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .use-case-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .use-case-card li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-11);
  }

  .use-case-card li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .how-to-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .how-to-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 64rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .how-to-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .how-to-card {
    background: var(--gray-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-4);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .how-to-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .how-to-card p {
    color: var(--gray-11);
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 2.5rem;
    background: var(--pink-10);
    color: var(--pink-1);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      background 0.2s,
      transform 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--pink-6);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  [data-animate-on-scroll] {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition:
      opacity 0.6s ease,
      transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  [data-animate-on-scroll].is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    const elements = document.querySelectorAll("[data-animate-on-scroll]");
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
      (entries) => {
        entries.forEach((entry) => {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add("is-visible");
            observer.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        });
      },
      { threshold: 0.1 }
    );

    elements.forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
  });
</script>
